      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Accordion -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="bg-black border border-[#1d92ea] rounded">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-captain text-white tracking-wide">No Subscriptions or Hidden Fees</summary>
        <p class="px-4 py-2 text-gray-300 font-captain">One-time install with full protection. No ongoing charges.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="bg-black border border-[#1d92ea] rounded">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-captain text-white tracking-wide">Compact and Discreet</summary>
        <p class="px-4 py-2 text-gray-300 font-captain">Installs easily and remains invisible to thieves.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="bg-black border border-[#1d92ea] rounded">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-captain text-white tracking-wide">Doesn’t Void Warranty</summary>
        <p class="px-4 py-2 text-gray-300 font-captain">Factory wiring remains untouched and compliant.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="bg-black border border-[#1d92ea] rounded">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-captain text-white tracking-wide">Blocks Engine and Transmission</summary>
        <p class="px-4 py-2 text-gray-300 font-captain">Stops operation without needing to cut into circuits.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 items-center gap-10 px-6 py-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div>
      <img src="/images/sched-igla-install.webp" alt="Schedule Installation" class="w-full rounded shadow-lg" />
    </div>
    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-cyber text-white mb-6">Schedule Your Installation</h2>
      <p class="text-[#1d92ea] font-captain tracking-[1.2px] max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Our certified team will assess your vehicle’s specific needs to determine the best IGLA solution for your setup — completely seamless, with no disruption to your factory wiring.
      </p>
      <Button href="/schedule" text="Schedule Your Install" variant="default" />
      <h2 class="mt-12 text-white font-kwajong text-base max-w-4xl mx-auto md:mx-0">
        Pricing varies depending on the vehicle and system version. We believe in full transparency, so our team is always available to provide a detailed breakdown and answer questions before you commit.
      </h2>
    </div>
  </section>
